add "go" infront of string from where thread needs to break;

WaitGroup, to wait until the thread is completed ,needs to be imported from sync 

import{
    "sync"
}

var wg = sync.WaitGroup

Sets the number of go routinesto wait for
 .(increase the counter by the provided number)
wg.Add(1) 

wait : blocks until the waitGroup counter 0
wg.wait()

wg.Done()